<h1 class="hero-h">A DTC meal-kit hyper-growth year that ended in a <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">HelloFresh acquisition.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">A Treetop fractional CMO engagement at Factor_ — the prepared-meal DTC brand that grew into one of the fastest-growing companies in America during the engagement window, named to the INC 5000 list in 2017 and 2018, and ultimately acquired by HelloFresh. The work: rebuild paid acquisition from $0 in spend to $4K+/day, cut blended CAC nearly in half, and lift lifecycle email revenue by an order of magnitude.</p>
